{"tid":651191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想上網識鬼妹嘅你，請進","createTime":"2018-05-03T02:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T23:46:41.000Z","uid":113697,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"489e46e1927979520818cddb885317849baa5900","tid":651191,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"(之前個post開錯台，重開)<br />\n見最近有一些男會員對認識鬼妹有興趣, 在此分享一下兩個比較出色嘅交友網站。<br />\n<br />\nHey-Ai<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/100250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F100250_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=05664c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n優點:<br />\n1. 絕大部份女會員都係鬼妹<br />\n2. 學術水平比較高(有很多相Amwf話題嘅帖可供參考, 例如佢哋喜歡亞洲男仕啲咩)<br />\n3. 女仕們學歷較高, 品格好<br />\n4.女仕們普遍對亞洲男仕和文化比較有興趣<br />\n<br />\n缺點:<br />\n英文書寫和閱讀能力要求較高<br />\n會員比較慢熱<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nInterpals<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/100300_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F100300_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0a392744&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n優點:<br />\n1.英文書寫和閱讀能力要求較低<br />\n2.搜索系統比較完善<br />\n3.會員人數較多<br />\n4.會員比較熱情<br />\n<br />\n缺點:<br />\n1.女仕們不一定對亞洲文化或男仕感趣<br />\n2.普遍語文能力較低,有可能出現溝通上嘅困難"},{"pid":"bf8b29c87b56531dfcf2289ded0ee5334441881f","tid":651191,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"賣廣告又賣得幾自然"},{"pid":"81c63b83968dcc5caee91e07c3e38e3337e4935d","tid":651191,"uid":113697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf8b29c87b56531dfcf2289ded0ee5334441881f","tid":651191,"uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"賣廣告又賣得幾自然"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"唔係賣廣告，兩個樓唔同公司開辦，同兩個都係免費。哩兩個係我用過最好的。"},{"pid":"a